.000Z","msg":"佢出黎受左佢就兩邊都皆大歡喜"},{"pid":"fbf7e3879a13cac61121bea78506dea2d1b04ea2","tid":1367260,"uid":216800,"like":193,"dislike":0,"score":193,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iVuvP5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iVuvP5.gif&h=9bc8a809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ce5213fc12e11f9cf8f9ec400bb1d84ed42765e","tid":1367260,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔理衝唔衝，都一定要出元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[緊急!!!!!!!!] 元朗極危險<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367206</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"527f61401beb20ebd47668d984299d2ff3be1ec9","tid":1367260,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fb5d50d3758a5142761762e6c526cc0f258f36f","tid":1367260,"uid":211461,"like":483,"dislike":6,"score":477,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"即係聽日有大鑊野<br />\n佢要事先講相反野撇清關係<br />\n聽日小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />high IQ"},{"pid":"a33e929417d005773fa82e45612f359c24d70890","tid":1367260,"uid":25794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"君妖出黎講真係令市民放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f7b074272303ee4f28ce5f500324bb9e2ca406","tid":1367260,"uid":274149,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">何妖出黎搞個握手會</span></span>"},{"pid":"b83127186191f67cd8014a4f5f7619a34573773c","tid":1367260,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"泛民可唔可以呼應公務員罷工 再提出全港大罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367211<