},{"pid":"f48552dcb16f95ef21aea9e68e22b1bd73d73ad3","tid":1367260,"uid":51814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府入面嘅暴徒聽住 ！<br />\n<br />\n如果香港市民嘅遊行活動裡面，有任何示威者被襲擊受傷甚至死亡嘅話，而你地冇全力協助防御拯救 ！<br />\n<br />\n即係代表你地唔能夠代表人民去保護人民嘅生命財產 ！<br />\n<br />\n咁你地只配得被自己生產嘅卵玷污 !<br />\n<br />\n睇下你地仲有乜卵用！<br />\n<br />\n自己計下條數，你地將會承受<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10,872,000次玷污</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n註1：毅進制遊行人數<br />\n6.9 ~ 24萬人<br />\n6.16 ~ 33.8萬人<br />\n7.1 ~ 19萬人<br />\n7.21 ~ 13.8萬人<br />\n每人1打中國雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n註2： 實際玷污次數應該係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">48,120,000次或以上</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/162524_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F162524_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif&h=7d78a2a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c64ef1eb7d96322eb78bfd344946d9ced3448f6f","tid":1367260,"uid":277034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"好威威，幾幫人都聽你話，黑白通吃‼️<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d67da614d4e1c6ccaad251f50f96708c243582","tid":1367260,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦何妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7851836e18642063190f977eb4d438d03f64d5d2","tid":1367260,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"何律師定何軍師?"},{"pid":"174d321327504ed8ebdb2710c9787c01626d7456","tid":1367260,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"龜縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e20795a40257fb5ecc648da3536f22a